if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先鑊要夠熱<br />\n然後儘可能引乾啲菇<br />\n同埋唔好咁早落鹽<br />\n炒到咁上下先落鹽再兜兩兜就起"},{"pid":"644dd4eeec21c8c51fe09367b2a05cda1dbdf0a3","tid":305104,"uid":113546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:24:20.000Z","msg":"煮白飯+小小藜麥係面一齊煮<br />\n藜麥有好高既蛋白質同b雜 仲有其他人體需要既營養<br />\nB雜對神經系統有益 個人會精神啲 同提升免疫系統都有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n藜麥好多地方都有得買 百佳見過70蚊500g 每次落2 3匙都有排用"},{"pid":"e21044623e601ec66eda3ba6852a8430dbce9f99","tid":305104,"uid":47480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T21:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煮白飯+小小藜麥係面一齊煮<br />\n藜麥有好高既蛋白質同b雜 仲有其他人體需要既營養<br />\nB雜對神經系統有益 個人會精神啲 同提升免疫系統都有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n藜麥好多地方都有得買 百佳見過70蚊500g 每次落2 3匙都有排用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未食過藜麥，試下先"},{"pid":"537df32da17e089bad49a8123b78ccbbc093c0d6","tid":305104,"uid":34838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:51:21.000Z","msg":"米線 菜心 烚蛋<br />\n<br />\n窮撚恩物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc6e6012ebf2ed19b58334f70c860dd26cd46da","tid":305104,"uid":47480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>米線 菜心 烚蛋<br />\n<br />\n窮撚恩物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n米線好易餓"},{"pid":"0c0feb42ef75a1f7cb3d412ea85ba551e3ecaec5","tid":305104,"uid":47480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電磁爐點解煎唔到蛋</blockquote><br />\n唔知係咪個煎pan 問題 唔識熱"},{"pid":"7f17c159617c11b6c13c3d38f5bf93f5132cf8ee","tid":305104,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"多寶集錦pizza"},{"pid":"20364867764dbfcb5301359543986880ee0ae604","tid":305104,"uid":1345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:45:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>電磁爐點解煎唔到蛋</blockquote><br />\n唔知係咪個煎pan 問題 唔識熱</blockquote><br />\n換個個pan啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260fb6652eda68ed9b79195d4959f268a4995a68","tid":305104,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>電磁爐點解煎唔到蛋</blockquote><br />\n唔知係咪個煎pan 問題 唔識熱</blockquote><br />\n有部分煎pan係電磁爐上面係唔識熱架<br />\n你要買寫明電磁爐可以用既煎pan<br />\n之前日本城特價 $60蚊一個好大既煎pan<br />\n我有一個電磁爐可以用既煎pan，之前住hall用既<br />\n巴打唔介意用二手野既話，我返到香港搵畀你呀<br />\n應該放左係屋企角落頭啲紙箱入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f08a2cc5889543960fed2fda4f1a799eac1272","tid":305104,"uid":37959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:12:57.000Z","msg":"薯仔 淥水餃"},{"pid":"9839eb5c3516c32bdbbab43e331abe305abf8bf0","tid":305104,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:14:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}